name: Factory Fresh Granada (Red Foot) Corona
additionalNotes:
ADMINS:  There are three lines of this cigar.  All three have the same fillers, but with different ratios.  This one contains 20% Habano, 10% Pele de Oro, and 70% Corojo Ligero.
